### Component 2: AI Engine Foundation (Person A)

#### [NEW] [src/services/aiService.js](file:///c:/Users/Lenovo/Desktop/Galactica/Galactia_hackathon/backend/src/services/aiService.js)
- `generateCode(prompt, fileContent, language, cursorLine)` — calls OpenAI/Claude
- `getAutoComplete(partialCode, fileContext, language)` — calls AI with lower temp (0.3)
- Provider abstraction: switch between OpenAI and Claude via config flag

#### [NEW] [src/prompts/generatePrompt.js](file:///c:/Users/Lenovo/Desktop/Galactica/Galactia_hackathon/backend/src/prompts/generatePrompt.js)
- PromptBuilder class with 4 sections: SYSTEM, CONTEXT, INSTRUCTION, FEW-SHOT
- Code generation system prompt template
- Temperature: 0.6, max tokens: 800

#### [NEW] [src/prompts/autocompletePrompt.js](file:///c:/Users/Lenovo/Desktop/Galactica/Galactia_hackathon/backend/src/prompts/autocompletePrompt.js)
- Autocomplete system prompt template
- Temperature: 0.3, max tokens: 400

#### [NEW] [src/routes/generate.js](file:///c:/Users/Lenovo/Desktop/Galactica/Galactia_hackathon/backend/src/routes/generate.js)
- `POST /api/v1/generate` — accepts prompt, file_content, language, cursor_line
- Validates input with Joi schema
- Returns: `{ code, explanation, language, tokens_used, insertion_point }`

#### [NEW] [src/routes/autocomplete.js](file:///c:/Users/Lenovo/Desktop/Galactica/Galactia_hackathon/backend/src/routes/autocomplete.js)
- `POST /api/v1/autocomplete` — accepts partial_code, file_context, language
- Returns: `{ suggestion, confidence, cached }`

