### Component 4: Frontend-Backend Connection

#### [NEW] [src/lib/api.js](file:///c:/Users/Lenovo/Desktop/Galactica/Galactia_hackathon/frontend/src/lib/api.js)
- API client functions: `generateCode()`, `getAutoComplete()`
- Base URL: `http://localhost:3000/api/v1`
- Include JWT token in Authorization header

#### First Integration Test
- User types prompt in AI panel → clicks Generate → frontend sends `POST /api/v1/generate` → backend calls OpenAI → response displayed in editor
- This validates the entire chain works end-to-end

