## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **AI Provider Choice**: The docs mention both OpenAI and Claude/Anthropic. Which AI provider do you want to use as the primary? This affects API key setup and SDK installation on Day 0.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Database Setup**: The architecture specifies PostgreSQL + Redis. For Day 0, do you want to:
> - (A) Set up PostgreSQL locally  
> - (B) Use a cloud service like Supabase/Neon for PostgreSQL  
> - (C) Start with SQLite/JSON file and migrate to PostgreSQL later  

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Code Execution Engine**: The docs mention Judge0 API. Do you want to:
> - (A) Use the hosted Judge0 API (requires RapidAPI key)  
> - (B) Self-host Judge0 via Docker  
> - (C) Defer execution feature to Day 3+ and focus on AI features first  

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Team Roles**: The schedule assumes Person A = Backend + AI/ML, Person B = Frontend. Can you confirm team member assignments and which role you (the reader) are playing?

